<h4>Course Description</h4>
<p>This course teaches the development of web-based interfaces for web applications using user-centered design and interaction patterns managed with dynamic database driven queries and advanced user feedback.  Addresses usability issues within complex web applications, making appropriate choices in system security and user management systems.  Throughout this couse, students will use PHP, MySQL, JavaScript, Jquery, HTML, and CSS to implement practical web applications. The course consists of a series of small web development assignments and a large course project.</p>